00:43.539 --> 00:45.072
Oh, there he is.

00:45.157 --> 00:47.658
Zach Morstein in the flesh,
boy genius inventor

00:47.726 --> 00:49.493
of the latest
get-laid-quick program

00:49.561 --> 00:51.162
for the socially challenged.

00:51.229 --> 00:53.564
What an honor.

00:53.615 --> 00:54.749
Hannah.

00:54.833 --> 00:56.918
Hannah had me sitting
in reception

00:57.002 --> 00:58.920
with my thumb
up my bum

00:59.004 --> 01:02.623
for 6 whole minutes,
which for me 5 minutes too long.

01:02.708 --> 01:05.760
Seekout.

01:05.844 --> 01:08.462
Is that the best name
you could come up with?

01:08.547 --> 01:10.715
Too weird to be a reporter,
too wrinkled to be an attorney.

01:10.766 --> 01:12.183
He says, referring
to the lawsuit

01:12.250 --> 01:14.886
which should by rights
having him changing his underwear

01:14.937 --> 01:16.137
3 times a day.

01:16.221 --> 01:20.224
So you founded the company
with these two,

01:20.275 --> 01:21.642
and then you nobbled
the one on the left,

01:21.727 --> 01:24.478
using some legal loophole,

01:24.563 --> 01:26.981
just before you were
about to make billions.

01:27.065 --> 01:29.884
And you enjoyed
every minute of it.

01:29.952 --> 01:32.570
You read micro-expressions.
I saw an article on that once.

01:32.621 --> 01:35.723
Kyle wouldn't risk his lawsuit
on some half-baked mindreader,

01:35.791 --> 01:37.792
so you must be working
for Claire.

01:39.461 --> 01:42.079
In all the time that you spent
developing this program,

01:42.130 --> 01:45.533
did it ever occur to you
to just buy a girl a drink?

01:45.601 --> 01:48.719
So I just...

01:48.787 --> 01:50.721
Point the phone

01:50.789 --> 01:52.340
at a girl that I fancy,

01:52.424 --> 01:54.809
then I sniff through
her laundry,

01:54.893 --> 01:56.143
just a little bit,

01:56.228 --> 01:58.295
until I figure out
what it takes

01:58.347 --> 01:59.630
to get into her panties.

01:59.681 --> 02:01.098
Excuse me?

02:01.149 --> 02:03.801
Claire and I have been
friends since freshman year.

02:03.852 --> 02:05.937
You can tell her
she's safe.

02:08.407 --> 02:10.491
Define safe.

02:10.591 --> 02:13.991
