02:14.079 --> 02:18.199
♪ dream,
send me a sign ♪

02:18.283 --> 02:21.151
♪ turn back the clock ♪

02:21.203 --> 02:23.220
♪ give me some time ♪

02:23.288 --> 02:26.257
♪ I need to break out ♪

02:26.324 --> 02:27.992
♪ make a new name ♪

02:28.043 --> 02:30.761
♪ let's open our eyes ♪

02:30.829 --> 02:35.833
♪ to the brand-new day ♪

